New Records: Zack Wheeler earned his 100th career victory.
Key Match Events: Zack Wheeler pitched seven shutout innings.
Edmundo Sosa homered and doubled, driving in two runs.
Trea Turner homered to left center.
Carlos Estevez earned his 23rd save with a scoreless inning.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was held at Citizens Bank Park with an attendance of 42,730.
The game lasted 2 hours and 16 minutes.
The Phillies won the regular season series 3-1 against the Braves.
